arguments.template:
<header class="{{theme}} bx--modal-header">
			<ng-content></ng-content>
			<button
				class="bx--modal-close"
				[attr.aria-label]="closeLabel"
				(click)="onClose()">
				<!-- old icon -->
				<svg
					*ngIf="!isExperimental"
					class="bx--modal-close__icon"
					fill-rule="evenodd"
					height="10"
					role="img"
					viewBox="0 0 10 10"
					width="10"
					[attr.aria-label]="closeLabel">
					<title>{{closeLabel}}</title>
					<path d="M6.32 5L10 8.68 8.68 10 5 6.32 1.32 10 0 8.68 3.68 5 0 1.32 1.32 0 5 3.68 8.68 0 10 1.32 6.32 5z"></path>
				</svg>
				<!-- new icon -->
				<svg
					*ngIf="isExperimental"
					focusable="false"
					preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet"
					style="will-change: transform;"
					xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
					class="bx--modal-close__icon"
					width="16"
					height="16"
					viewBox="0 0 16 16"
					aria-hidden="true">
					<path
						d="M12 4.7l-.7-.7L8 7.3 4.7 4l-.7.7L7.3 8 4 11.3l.7.7L8 8.7l3.3 3.3.7-.7L8.7 8z">
					</path>
				</svg>
			</button>
		</header>
